cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the issue of spreadsheet errors and proposes ways to reduce them, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the need for cell-by-cell code inspection, which is a technique used in programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper discusses the human-computer interaction aspect of spreadsheet errors (cs.HC) and the need for further research (cs.CY). Finally, the paper touches on the topic of cybersecurity (cs.CR) as spreadsheet errors can lead to security breaches.
